Resume Filter

CLI modes

- Sample mode: rank up to 100 uploaded candidates with live embeddings.
	- `python rank.py --candidate-mode sample --candidates-path data/sample_candidates.json --candidate-limit 100`
- Pool mode: rank the 100k candidate pool using precomputed embeddings.
	- `python rank.py --candidate-mode pool --candidates-path data/candidates.jsonl --embeddings-path artifacts/candidate_embeddings.npy --ids-path artifacts/candidate_ids.npy`

Embedding build

- `python scripts/build_embeddings.py --input data/candidates.jsonl --output-embeddings artifacts/candidate_embeddings.npy --output-ids artifacts/candidate_ids.npy`

Hugging Face / Streamlit app

- Run locally with `streamlit run app.py`
- The app accepts JD uploads and either a sample JSON candidate file or a pool JSONL candidate file.
